<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>生活 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/</link><description>Recent content in 生活 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2025 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 04 Oct 2023 07:35:11 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><follow_challenge><feedId>42331815237783556</feedId><userId>41909911558319104</userId></follow_challenge><item><title>无题</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/20231004/</link><pubDate>Wed, 04 Oct 2023 07:35:11 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/20231004/</guid><description>母亲围地养了十几只鸡，父亲常坐爷爷留下的竹椅沉思，偶尔抽自种草烟。秋日凉风轻拂，鸟鸣溪流声清晰可闻。夜晚宁静深沉，充满禅意。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/20231004/featured.png"/></item><item><title>孤独真的能毁掉一个人吗？</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/lonely/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 May 2017 00:01:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/lonely/</guid><description>面对姐姐对冷漠的质疑，作者回忆起与放牛老人的温情互动，却只用一声哦回应死讯。孤独源于看透社交表演的无趣结尾，而真实自我曾吓退人群。如今选择与孤独为伴，并非标榜高尚，而是拥抱自由的生活方式。毁灭前，唯有孤独能赋予千万种可能。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/lonely/featured.png"/></item><item><title>探讨我的健康网络生活</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/netwalking/</link><pubDate>Thu, 10 Feb 2011 20:46:22 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/netwalking/</guid><description>网络已成为生活必需品，但过度沉迷需自我约束。非 IT 从业者应合理规划上网时间，聚焦核心需求如邮件、博客、资讯，避免无意义的资源搜索、软件试用和被动聊天。反思发现，发呆反而是唯一有价值的时刻，因为促发了思考。过去多年的网络行为本质未变，只是工具升级，缺乏实质性进步。环境塑造习惯，在无法改变现状时，唯有通过严格时间管理减少屏幕时间，才能提升生活质量。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/netwalking/featured.png"/></item><item><title>为什么我会突然热情锐减</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/myenthusiasm/</link><pubDate>Thu, 10 Feb 2011 02:41:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/myenthusiasm/</guid><description>内心酝酿已久的计划迟迟未行动，无论是更换主题、旅行还是写作都停留在空想阶段。电影、音乐、阅读和运动等日常乐趣逐渐消失，生活变得单调乏味，连曾经的游戏热情也消退了。这种状态令人浮躁却难以改变，唯有从调整生活习惯开始重拾激情！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/myenthusiasm/featured.png"/></item><item><title>我要找老婆</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/im-looking-for-my-wife/</link><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jan 2011 17:50:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/im-looking-for-my-wife/</guid><description>选购商品如同寻找伴侣，关键指标决定长期满意度。电脑看配置，手机重性能，域名需信誉，空间求稳定。车子认品牌，房子挑地段，衣服重质量，鞋子考耐磨，饮食合口味。每个选择都需精准匹配需求！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/im-looking-for-my-wife/featured.png"/></item><item><title>富足的时间 肤浅的生活</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/imsnail/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Mar 2010 03:26:15 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/imsnail/</guid><description>富足的时间与肤浅的生活交织，未来模糊不清，过往混乱不堪，还有无数擦肩而过的爱情！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/imsnail/featured.png"/></item><item><title>有种生活，有种心态</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/kind-of-life-a-kind-of-mentality/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2006 09:52:40 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/kind-of-life-a-kind-of-mentality/</guid><description>高二那年与师长的冲突和转学失败成为人生转折点，曾经的乐观少年逐渐陷入抑郁与自我封闭。心理测试显示存在明显心理问题，如今仅对 CS 游戏保持狂热，拒绝恋爱只因对方不懂 CS。虽怀念初恋的温暖，却坚持寻找会打 CS 的女孩并相信真爱。曾受自杀念头困扰，现沉迷游戏与痞子蔡的文字，生活只剩虚拟世界的慰藉！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/kind-of-life-a-kind-of-mentality/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>